data.description: Charming 2-Bedroom, 1-Bath Home With Versatile Bonus Room, Wood Interior And Sliding Wood Doors. Welcome To This Cozy Retreat Offering A Flexible Layout With A Potential Bunk Room Or Office Space, Perfect For Your Personalized Needs. Nestled In A Serene Setting, This Property Boasts A Spacious 40x30 Insulated Garage, An Additional Storage Shed, And A Long Driveway Ensuring Privacy And Tranquility. Surrounded By Farmland, This Home Invites You To Embrace Peaceful Living With No Neighbors To The Front Or Back. Don't Miss The Chance To Make This Idyllic Haven Your Own! This Home Is Minutes From Angels Gate With Access To To Fort Campbell Army Air Field. Go Home After PT Or Hangout AT Home For Lunch!
